m/nixappimage/nixpkgs/stable/neovim:0.11.2-x86_64-linuxdsizee32 MBdbsumx@f673d194cdcad8175184f3fcd3b089d1abf23c0d490482a4ef13fbdee2ef29f6fshasumx@e13600a6105827fabff590fb01f283f6af088efd3861c1ab9ba348c85ef0cec4jbuild_datet2025-06-01T19:15:01Zhsrc_urls¹x https://github.com/neovim/neovimhweb_urls²qhttps://neovim.iorhttps://neovim.orglbuild_scriptx^https://github.com/pkgforge/soarpkgs/blob/main/packages/neovim/nixappimage.nixpkgs.stable.yamlibuild_logx³https://api.ghcr.pkgforge.dev/pkgforge/pkgcache/neovim/nixappimage/nixpkgs/stable/neovim?tag=0.11.2-x86_64-linux&download=neovim.logjcategoriesrUtility,TextEditorisnapshots³Δfcommits0.10.3-x86_64-linuxgversionf0.10.3Δfcommits0.10.4-x86_64-linuxgversionf0.10.4Δfcommits0.11.0-x86_64-linuxgversionf0.11.0Δfcommits0.11.1-x86_64-linuxgversionf0.11.1hprovideslneovim=>nvimglicense¹jApache-2.0kmaintainersx*Azathothas (https://github.com/Azathothas)enotes³xDBuilt Using Nixpkgs. Check/Report @ https://github.com/NixOS/nixpkgsxQPacked Using NixAppImage. Check/Report @ https://github.com/pkgforge/nix-appimagexCLearn more @ https://docs.pkgforge.dev/formats/packages/nixappimagex[PORTABLE] (Works on AnyLinux)drank…lweb_manifestx]https://pkgs.pkgforge.dev/repo/pkgcache/x86_64-linux/neovim/nixappimage/nixpkgs/stable/neovimΗcpkgxsimplex-desktop.nixappimagehpkg_nameosimplex-desktopfpkg_idxnixpkgs.simplex-chat-desktopfapp_idtchat.simplex.simplexdiconxyhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/chat/simplex/simplex/6a1eb8b6aea47e919afb6ac3f90306be/icons/128x128/chat.simplex.simplex.pngkdescriptionxLDesktop application for SimpleX Chat, A 100% private-by-design chat platformpdescription_longySimpleX - the first messaging platform that has no user identifiers, not even random numbers!

 Security assessment was done by Trail of Bits in November 2022.

 SimpleX Chat features:

 
end-to-end encrypted messages, with editing, replies and deletion of messages. 
sending end-to-end encrypted images and files. 
single-use and long-term user addresses. 
secret chat groups - only group members know it exists and who is the member. 
end-to-end encrypted audio and video calls. 
private instant notifications. 
portable chat profile - you can transfer your chat contacts and history to another device (terminal or mobile). 
 

SimpleX Chat advantages:

 
Full privacy of your identity, profile, contacts and metadata: unlike any other existing messaging platform, SimpleX uses no phone numbers or any other identifiers assigned to the users - not even random numbers. This protects the privacy of who you are communicating with, hiding it from SimpleX platform servers and from any observers. 
Complete protection against spam and abuse: as you have no identifier on SimpleX platform, you cannot be contacted unless you share a one-time invitation link or an optional temporary user address. 
Full ownership, control and security of your data: SimpleX stores all user data on client devices, the messages are only held temporarily on SimpleX relay servers until they are received. 
Decentralized network: you can use SimpleX with your own servers and still communicate with people using the servers that are pre-configured in the apps or any other SimpleX servers. 
 

You can connect to anybody you know via link or scan QR code (in the video call or in person) and start sending messages instantly - no emails, phone numbers or passwords needed.

 Your profile and contacts are only stored in the app on your device - our servers do not have access to this information.

 All messages are end-to-end encrypted using open-source double-ratchet protocol; the messages are routed via our servers using open-source SimpleX Messaging Protocol.kscreenshots¹xohttps://dl.flathub.org/media/chat/simplex/simplex/6a1eb8b6aea47e919afb6ac3f90306be/screenshots/image-1_orig.pnggversione6.3.4ldownload_urlxmoci://ghcr.io/pkgforge/pkgcache/simplex-desktop/nixappimage/nixpkgs/stable/simplex-desktop:6.3.4-x86_64-linuxdsizef523 MBdbsumx@f3354bddaed65ce9bdbfe219dfcc07f31cdda62ac906def9ff758f8c8ee40eb1fshasumx@9419c11ec8044ca06a8e64ca4a5015292d983ec53e496b44be1d801a6b74cbc9jbuild_datet2025-05-20T19:40:21Zhsrc_urls¹x,https://github.com/simplex-chat/simplex-chathweb_urls²thttps://simplex.chatx,https://github.com/simplex-chat/simplex-chatlbuild_scriptxghttps://github.com/pkgforge/soarpkgs/blob/main/packages/simplex-desktop/nixappimage.nixpkgs.stable.yamlibuild_logxûhttps://api.ghcr.pkgforge.dev/pkgforge/pkgcache/simplex-desktop/nixappimage/nixpkgs/stable/simplex-desktop?tag=6.3.4-x86_64-linux&download=simplex-desktop.logjcategoriesxUtility,Chat,InstantMessagingisnapshotsÜΔfcommitr6.2.3-x86_64-linuxgversione6.2.3Δfcommitr6.2.4-x86_64-linuxgversione6.2.4Δfcommitr6.2.5-x86_64-linuxgversione6.2.5Δfcommitr6.3.1-x86_64-linuxgversione6.3.1Δfcommitr6.3.2-x86_64-linuxgversione6.3.2Δfcommitr6.3.3-x86_64-linuxgversione6.3.3hprovidesx%simplex-desktop==simplex-chat-desktopglicense¹hAGPL-3.0kmaintainersx*Azathothas (https://github.com/Azathothas)enotes³xDBuilt Using Nixpkgs. Check/Report @ https://github.com/NixOS/nixpkgsxQPacked Using NixAppImage. Check/Report @ https://github.com/pkgforge/nix-appimagexCLearn more @ https://docs.pkgforge.dev/formats/packages/nixappimagex[PORTABLE] (Works on AnyLinux)drankθlweb_manifestxohttps://pkgs.pkgforge.dev/repo/pkgcache/x86_64-linux/simplex-desktop/nixappimage/nixpkgs/stable/simplex-desktopΗcpkgxtelegram-desktop.nixappimagehpkg_nameptelegram-desktopfpkg_idxnixpkgs.telegram-desktopfapp_idtorg.telegram.desktopdiconxyhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/telegram/desktop/f6d612c5d71a9559f525f38839914a63/icons/128x128/org.telegram.desktop.pngkdescriptionx2Official desktop version of Telegram messaging apppdescription_longy
1Pure instant messaging βÄî simple, fast, secure, and synced across all your devices. One of the world's top 10 most downloaded apps with over 500 million active users.

 FAST: Telegram is the fastest messaging app on the market, connecting people via a unique, distributed network of data centers around the globe.

 SYNCED: You can access your messages from all your phones, tablets and computers at once. Telegram apps are standalone, so you donβÄôt need to keep your phone connected. Start typing on one device and finish the message from another. Never lose your data again.

 UNLIMITED: You can send media and files, without any limits on their type and size. Your entire chat history will require no disk space on your device, and will be securely stored in the Telegram cloud for as long as you need it.

 SECURE: We made it our mission to provide the best security combined with ease of use. Everything on Telegram, including chats, groups, media, etc. is encrypted using a combination of 256-bit symmetric AES encryption, 2048-bit RSA encryption, and DiffieβÄ™Hellman secure key exchange.

 100% FREE & OPEN: Telegram has a fully documented and free API for developers, open source apps and verifiable builds to prove the app you download is built from the exact same source code that is published.

 POWERFUL: You can create group chats with up to 200,000 members, share large videos, documents of any type (.DOCX, .MP3, .ZIP, etc.) up to 2 GB each, and even set up bots for specific tasks. Telegram is the perfect tool for hosting online communities and coordinating teamwork.

 RELIABLE: Built to deliver your messages using as little data as possible, Telegram is the most reliable messaging system ever made. It works even on the weakest mobile connections.

 FUN: Telegram has powerful photo and video editing tools, animated stickers and emoji, fully customizable themes to change the appearance of your app, and an open sticker/GIF platform to cater to all your expressive needs.

 SIMPLE: While providing an unprecedented array of features, we take great care to keep the interface clean. Telegram is so simple you already know how to use it.

 PRIVATE: We take your privacy seriously and will never give any third parties access to your data. You can delete any message you ever sent or received for both sides, at any time and without a trace. Telegram will never use your data to show you ads.

 We keep expanding the boundaries of what you can do with a messaging app. DonβÄôt wait years for older messengers to catch up with Telegram βÄî join the revolution today.kscreenshots¹xohttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/telegram/desktop/f6d612c5d71a9559f525f38839914a63/screenshots/image-1_orig.pnggversionf5.13.1ldownload_urlxpoci://ghcr.io/pkgforge/pkgcache/telegram-desktop/nixappimage/nixpkgs/stable/telegram-desktop:5.13.1-x86_64-linuxdsizef395 MBdbsumx@0f1ed818813a2374626bd1277a7b33aa67b9dfb64557bf5476d8f9b9f21c67affshasumx@10d3611a2e8823d4ca0c2ded5a89ce70bd1c3f154d1f27af95ddbc104a76d495jbuild_datet2025-04-20T19:32:12Zhsrc_urls¹x+https://github.com/telegramdesktop/tdesktophweb_urls²xhttps://desktop.telegram.orgx+https://github.com/telegramdesktop/tdesktoplbuild_scriptxhhttps://github.com/pkgforge/soarpkgs/blob/main/packages/telegram-desktop/nixappimage.nixpkgs.stable.yamlibuild_logxΔhttps://api.ghcr.pkgforge.dev/pkgforge/pkgcache/telegram-desktop/nixappimage/nixpkgs/stable/telegram-desktop?tag=5.13.1-x86_64-linux&download=telegram-desktop.logjcategoriesxNetwork,InstantMessagingisnapshotsÖΔfcommits5.10.2-x86_64-linuxgversionf5.10.2Δfcommits5.10.3-x86_64-linuxgversionf5.10.3Δfcommits5.10.5-x86_64-linuxgversionf5.10.5Δfcommits5.10.7-x86_64-linuxgversionf5.10.7Δfcommits5.11.1-x86_64-linuxgversionf5.11.1hprovidesx"telegram-desktop==Telegram-Desktopglicense¹gGPL-3.0kmaintainersx*Azathothas (https://github.com/Azathothas)enotes³xDBuilt Using Nixpkgs. Check/Report @ https://github.com/NixOS/nixpkgsxQPacked Using NixAppImage. Check/Report @ https://github.com/pkgforge/nix-appimagexCLearn more @ https://docs.pkgforge.dev/formats/packages/nixappimagex[PORTABLE] (Works on AnyLinux)drankωlweb_manifestxqhttps://pkgs.pkgforge.dev/repo/pkgcache/x86_64-linux/telegram-desktop/nixappimage/nixpkgs/stable/telegram-desktopΗcpkgtchromium.nixappimagehpkg_namehchromiumfpkg_idxnixpkgs.ungoogled-chromiumfapp_idx/io.github.ungoogled_software.ungoogled_chromiumdiconx·https://dl.flathub.org/media/io/github/ungoogled_software.ungoogled_chromium/08ff5f12864ce878e2c5d1ec094329e0/icons/128x128/io.github.ungoogled_software.ungoogled_chromium.pngkdescriptionxaOpen source web browser from Google, with dependencies on Google web services removed (Ungoogled)pdescription_longyuUngoogled Chromium is Google Chromium, sans dependency on Google web services. It also features some tweaks to enhance privacy, control, and transparency (almost all of which require manual activation or enabling).

 Ungoogled Chromium retains the default Chromium experience as closely as possible. Unlike other Chromium forks that have their own visions of a web browser, Ungoogled Chromium is essentially a drop-in replacement for Chromium.

 Without signing in to a Google Account, Chromium does pretty well in terms of security and privacy. However, Chromium still has some dependency on Google web services and binaries. In addition, Google designed Chromium to be easy and intuitive for users, which means they compromise on transparency and control of inner operations.

 Ungoogled Chromium addresses these issues in the following ways:

 
Remove all remaining background requests to any web services while building and running the browser 
Remove all code specific to Google web services 
Remove all uses of pre-made binaries from the source code, and replace them with user-provided alternatives when possible 
Disable features that inhibit control and transparency, and add or modify features that promote them (these changes will almost always require manual activation or enabling) 
 

These features are implemented as configuration flags, patches, and custom scripts.kscreenshotsÉxähttps://dl.flathub.org/media/io/github/ungoogled_software.ungoogled_chromium/08ff5f12864ce878e2c5d1ec094329e0/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngxähttps://dl.flathub.org/media/io/github/ungoogled_software.ungoogled_chromium/08ff5f12864ce878e2c5d1ec094329e0/screenshots/image-2_orig.pngxähttps://dl.flathub.org/media/io/github/ungoogled_software.ungoogled_chromium/08ff5f12864ce878e2c5d1ec094329e0/screenshots/image-3_orig.pnggversionm137.0.7151.55ldownload_urlxjoci://ghcr.io/pkgforge/pkgcache/chromium/nixappimage/nixpkgs/ungoogled/chromium:137.0.7151.55-x86_64-linuxdsizef365 MBdbsumx@1143c23b59aa9e9189c0d49a3c54061d6e20ec1dc1816f21ebbe99fa1c2a7066fshasumx@5f1e0cfc9fbe4d79793dbf4dc94a15e469ab1b71e9c715fde8159efbbd53c0b7jbuild_datet2025-05-30T19:18:14Zhsrc_urls¹x8https://github.com/ungoogled-software/ungoogled-chromiumlbuild_scriptxchttps://github.com/pkgforge/soarpkgs/blob/main/packages/chromium/nixappimage.nixpkgs.ungoogled.yamlibuild_logxîhttps://api.ghcr.pkgforge.dev/pkgforge/pkgcache/chromium/nixappimage/nixpkgs/ungoogled/chromium?tag=137.0.7151.55-x86_64-linux&download=chromium.logjcategoriesx(Network,WebBrowser,WebDevelopment,ViewerisnapshotsçΔfcommitx131.0.6778.264-x86_64-linuxgversionn131.0.6778.264Δfcommitx132.0.6834.83-x86_64-linuxgversionm132.0.6834.83Δfcommitx132.0.6834.110-x86_64-linuxgversionn132.0.6834.110Δfcommitx132.0.6834.159-x86_64-linuxgversionn132.0.6834.159Δfcommitx133.0.6943.53-x86_64-linuxgversionm133.0.6943.53Δfcommitx133.0.6943.98-x86_64-linuxgversionm133.0.6943.98Δfcommitx133.0.6943.126-x86_64-linuxgversionn133.0.6943.126Δfcommitx133.0.6943.141-x86_64-linuxgversionn133.0.6943.141Δfcommitx134.0.6998.35-x86_64-linuxgversionm134.0.6998.35Δfcommitx135.0.7049.95-x86_64-linuxgversionm135.0.7049.95Δfcommitx135.0.7049.114-x86_64-linuxgversionn135.0.7049.114Δfcommitx136.0.7103.59-x86_64-linuxgversionm136.0.7103.59Δfcommitx136.0.7103.113-x86_64-linuxgv