 emulator and multiplexerpdescription_longyWezTerm is a terminal emulator with support for modern features such as fonts with ligatures, hyperlinks, multiple windows, tabs and split panes.

Configuration is expressed using Lua and many powerful functions are provided to help you customize your terminal to your workflow.

